{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"9eaf5dc853","title":"给李济深的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"90c7b8641c","index":0,"year":1936,"month":9,"day":23,"articleId":"9eaf5dc853"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji9-1","name":"毛泽东全集第9卷(1)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji9-1.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji9-1":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"453dc76182","type":"paragraph","text":"给李济深的信！","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"9eaf5dc853"},{"id":"adf7e27abb","type":"paragraph","text":"（1936年9月23日）","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"9eaf5dc853"},{"id":"bda0acd8c9","type":"paragraph","text":"国难如斯，非有几个纯洁无私之政治集团及许多限苦奋斗之仁人志士为全国各党各派各界各军之中坚，伟大的反日统一战线之真正完成与坚持斗争，是不能容易达到目的的。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"9eaf5dc853"},{"id":"fb0137268c","type":"paragraph","text":"[1]1936年9月23日，毛泽东致信李济深，希望李济深和李宗仁、白崇禧派遣政治上负责人员来陕，能有专人常驻，沟通情意。这是该信的主要内容。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"9eaf5dc853"}],"page":{"id":"07060c28b7","publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"9eaf5dc853","start":164,"end":164}}}},"__N_SSG":true}